text: Waco () is a city in McLennan County, Texas. The city has an estimated 2023 population of 144,816.Waco at City Data ==Attractions== Major Waco attractions include: * Armstrong Browning Library * Baylor University * Cameron Park Zoo * Dr Pepper Museum * Lake Waco * Grand Lodge of Texas * Mayborn Museum Complex * The Ranger wing of the Commemorative Air Force * Texas Ranger Hall of Fame and Museum * Texas Sports Hall of Fame * Texas State Technical College * Waco Mammoth Site Waco Mammoth Site * Waco Suspension Bridge == References == Category:County seats in Texas
title: Waco, Texas
